        "id": "theory-card-1",
        "title": "So and such",
        "subtitle": "So and such",
        "cardType": "rule_card",
        "sections": [
          {
            "type": "comparison_table",
            "title": "Use",
            "headers": [
              "Use",
              "Example"
            ],
            "rows": [
              [
                "We use **so ... that** and **such ... that** to express a cause and its result — the first part explains the reason, and the second part shows the consequence.",
                "The film was **so scary** that I couldn't sleep."
              ]
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "form_table",
